PrecisAuthority (a) to accept the surrender of a lease (No. 139698) held by UPPER HUMBER GOLF CLUB INC. with respect to some 4.04 hectares of land situate on the grounds of DEER LAKE AIRPORT at Deer Lake, Newfoundland, and (b) to lease some 44.5 hectares of airport land to the golf club, for a term of forty (40) years, for the construction, operation, etc., of an 18-hole public golf course.
